      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The manticore is teriomorphic through and through: its triple rows of teeth, devouring appetite for human flesh, and lion's body concentrate the predatory jaws and feral chaos that define the symbol across every source."
      },
      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": {
