      },
      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The lethal cry is formless sonic terror erupting from the unknown, enacting the nyctomorphic voracity of night that dissolves the listener into the abyss."
      },
